          "params": [],
          "returnType": null,
          "description": "Map from Wang bitmask to local tile ID within the tileset. For blob mode (8-neighbor), keys are 0–255; the 47 valid combinations of the blob encoding must be covered at minimum. For edge mode (4-neighbor), keys are 0–15. Accepts either a ReadonlyMap or a plain Record<number, number>."
        },
